msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Man, RIZAP's the real deal, huh?\r\nTotally proved me wrong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "It's pretty freaking amazing.\r\nI mean, check out this slim body!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "And you used to be a real chubfest, too.\r\nNice, RIZAP! Think I should join up too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "For sure, for sure!\r\nYou're not gonna regret it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "RIZAP...\r\nI've heard a lot about this gym lately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "All right, I'll see what this is all about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Hm? Can I help you, sir?\r\nAre you interested in joining our gym?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, nah.\r\nI just wanted to see what it's about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Very well, sir. We usually ask for\r\nappointments, but I've got a moment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Right this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "This is where you check in, sir."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Great, thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "RIZAP... I've heard a lot about this gym lately.\r\nShould I head in?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Welcome, sir!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "This is, uh... my first time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "So you're a new customer.\r\nThen first, let me explain how we do things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "We're a membership-based gym, outfitted with dozens\r\nof private training rooms and state-of-the-art equipment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Members only, huh?\r\nI need to join?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Yep! First you'll need to undergo\r\na free counseling session."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Based on that session, we then create\r\na personalized training plan, just for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "If you like what we have on offer,\r\nyou'll be able to register right then and there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Interesting. So I get free counseling,\r\nthen decide whether or not I wanna join..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "All right then, I'll give it a shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Great, let me go get your counselor, sir.\r\nPlease take a seat over there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Sure, no prob."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Thank you for waiting, sir."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "I'll be both your counselor and trainer.\r\nThe name's Makuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Wait, you're the trainer, too?\r\nAnyway, I'm Kazuma Kiryu. Good to meet you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, then? Great name.\r\nYou're already in great shape, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Such finely toned muscles!\r\nI'll have to beef up my training to match you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "R-Right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Now then, let me tell you just\r\nhow things go down here at RIZAP."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Please do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "As our receptionist mentioned,\r\nwe're known for our private training rooms."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Each member gets one-on-one care from a trainer,\r\nresulting in absolutely out of this world service!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Oh, and you can change trainers whenever you want!\r\nFind the one that suits your style!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "That option sounds kinda appealing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "One more thing we offer here<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>\r\nWe also include free diet advice to help you slim down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "So you do training...\r\n<font_kind=yakuza_italic>And</font_kind> you plan my meals?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "That's right. Our dietitians work 'round the clock\r\nto offer only the best tips for maximum gains!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "I mean, a customer who never eats protein would\r\nnever get the rippling muscles he desires, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Our training and diet tips are absolutely vital for\r\ngetting the most out of your experience."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "True enough.\r\nI guess you have a point there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Now then, a training session and a diet plan\r\ncombine to form one round of the RIZAP Challenge."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "As a member of our gym, you'll have the opportunity\r\nto take on 12 whole RIZAP Challenge rounds."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "And that's the whole RIZAP experience!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Great. Sounds pretty useful."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Now then, let's head to the counseling room!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Your answers'll help us map out your training plan,\r\nso be sure to tell the truth!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I can do that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Well, that concludes the assessment.\r\nThe counseling part of our training is now over!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "I have the perfect regimen for you, Kiryu-san.\r\nCome on, take a look!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Wow, it actually looks pretty good.\r\nI'm impressed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Don't be.\r\nTraining you right is just part of my job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Anyway, Kiryu-san...\r\nHow do you feel about joining us?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "A RIZAP membership...\r\nWhat should I do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "I'll join.\r\nTraining like this is too good to resist."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Ah, thank you very much!\r\nI'll process your membership right away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "(I don't have enough money...\r\nMaybe I should come back later.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but I think I'll pass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "I see.\r\nThat's quite a shame..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Please come back if you change your mind, though.\r\nWe'll welcome you with open arms!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Great. Looking forward to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "(I should talk to the RIZAP trainer\r\nagain if I want to join.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Welcome, sir.\r\nHow can I help you today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "I'm looking to join RIZAP.\r\nIs that all right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Ah, but of course!\r\nI'll process your membership right away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "(I don't have enough money...\r\nMaybe I should come back later.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Actually, I don't need anything right now.\r\nSorry to bother you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Understood.\r\nJust let me know if you want to bulk up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Thank you again for joining us!\r\nIn case you forgot, I'm your trainer, Makuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Right. Looking forward to starting up.\r\nGive me everything you've got, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "But of course!\r\nDon't forget, I'm the best trainer in town!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Your muscles'll slice through diamonds\r\nonce I'm through with you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah... Nice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Now then, let me explain\r\njust how you train here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Whenever you're in the mood,\r\ncome talk to me here at RIZAP HQ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Then once you pick your routine of choice,\r\nthe sweat will start flowing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Ah, by the way, one session will\r\nconsist of two separate training routines."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Got it. So when I want to train,\r\nI just drop by and talk to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "That's right! Don't forget, there'll be\r\ndietary advice after each session as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "But we can talk about that when we come to it.\r\nI think I've crammed enough info in here already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Now then, let's get sweating!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!\r\nAre you ready to start training?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Yeah, let's do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "To the training room, then!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Tell me, Kiryu-san.\r\nWhat routine would you like to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Let's go with this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Perfect!\r\nTo the training room!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Nah, not right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Understood. Please come back\r\nwhen you're in the mood!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "Tell me, Kiryu-san!\r\nWhich routine comes next?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "This one looks good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Perfect!\r\nJust give me a second to set up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "All right, that's it for today's session!\r\nNow let's see how you did..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "That was perfect, Kiryu-san!\r\nYou must be in excellent shape!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "You did a great job!\r\nNo slacking though<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>try even harder next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Things really didn't go so well, huh?\r\nRelax, recharge, and try harder next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "Next, let's talk about your diet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you should eat whatever\r\nyou think is the healthiest option."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Oh, but be sure to take photos of your food!\r\nAnd don't forget to send them to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Only then will I be able to assess whether\r\nor not your diet is on the right track."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>I</font_kind> have to decide?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "I thought you'd be the one telling me\r\nwhat I'm supposed to eat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "I certainly <font_kind=yakuza_italic>could</font_kind> do that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "But if you don't form the right eating habits now,\r\nRIZAP's training will never help you slim down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "As your trainer and mentor,\r\nit's vital that I guide you toward a healthy future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Huh. You're actually pretty legit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Didn't I tell you?\r\nI'm the best trainer in town!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Although, I imagine most people don't\r\nhave a grasp on what the healthiest options are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "That's why I'll be dropping hints for you.\r\nFollow them carefully to boost your training to the max!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "All right, then. Sounds good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Now then, let's talk about your diet!\r\nYour recommendation for today is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "I'll also text my hints to the number you\r\nprovided upon registering as a RIZAP member."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Farewell, Kiryu-san!\r\nYou can do it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "What's up, Kiryu-san?\r\nYou should be out eating!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Please come see me once you're finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Welcome back, Kiryu-san!\r\nLet's see how that meal of yours was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Now then, let's see how this round\r\nof the RIZAP Challenge turned out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "That was fantastic, Kiryu-san!\r\nBoth your diet and training were flawless!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Your training was absolutely perfect,\r\nand your meal was well-balanced, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Your training was absolutely perfect,\r\nbut watch what you eat next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "Your training was absolutely perfect,\r\nbut, uh... your diet leaves a lot to be desired."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "I can't complain much about your diet!\r\nYour training was pretty good, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "It turned out pretty good overall!\r\nGive it 110% next time, though!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Your training was really impressive,\r\nbut your diet could use a little work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Your training was definitely good,\r\nbut watch what you eat next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Your diet was wonderful! Now just tighten up\r\nyour training and you'll be all set!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Your diet turned out great!\r\nNow just put some more effort into training..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "You should try a little harder during training!\r\nAnd maybe in your diet as well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "You have issues on both sides of things...\r\nbut with my help, we'll hammer them out in no time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "Now then, that brings our first round\r\nof the RIZAP Challenge to an end!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "How do you feel, Kiryu-san?\r\nIs RIZAP everything you hoped it would be?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Let me see...\r\nI guess I <font_kind=yakuza_italic>do</font_kind> feel a little more toned."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "That's great news!\r\nYou're one step closer to that diamond-cutting body!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "But it's important to rest as well.\r\nYou should hold off a while until your next session."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "All right, I'll come back later.\r\nLet's keep this going strong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Of course! With my help,\r\nyou'll have the finest body in all of Kamurocho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "We're committed to results, after all.\r\nThat's RIZAP's mission statement!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "Committed to results, huh? I can tell.\r\nI hope it makes a difference."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "As do I!\r\nWell, keep up the hard work!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "(I should hold off on training until\r\nI see my results from the last session.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Welcome back, Kiryu-san!\r\nAre you looking to train today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "Excellent!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Nah, not right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "I see.\r\nPlease come again if you have the time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "All right, that's it for today's session!\r\nNow let's see how you did..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "You did a great job!\r\nNo slacking though<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>try even harder next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah, this was a great session!\r\nLet's aim even higher next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Things really didn't go so well, huh?\r\nRelax, recharge, and try harder next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Now then, let's talk about your diet!\r\nYour recommendation for today is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Farewell, Kiryu-san!\r\nYou can do it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "What's up, Kiryu-san?\r\nYou should be out eating!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "Please come see me once you're finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Welcome back, Kiryu-san!\r\nLet's see how that meal of yours was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Now then, let's see how this round\r\nof the RIZAP Challenge turned out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "That was fantastic, Kiryu-san!\r\nBoth your diet and training were flawless!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Your training was absolutely perfect,\r\nand your meal was well-balanced, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Your training was absolutely perfect,\r\nbut watch what you eat next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "Your training was absolutely perfect,\r\nbut, uh... your diet leaves a lot to be desired."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "I can't complain much about your diet!\r\nYour training was pretty good, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "It turned out pretty good overall!\r\nGive it 110% next time, though!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Your training was really impressive,\r\nbut your diet could use a little work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Your training was definitely good,\r\nbut watch what you eat next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Your diet was wonderful! Now just tighten up\r\nyour training and you'll be all set!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Your diet turned out great!\r\nNow just put some more effort into training..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "You should try a little harder during training!\r\nAnd maybe in your diet as well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "You have issues on both sides of things...\r\nbut with my help, we'll hammer them out in no time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "That concludes today's RIZAP Challenge.\r\nNicely done!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Wow, Kiryu-san!\r\nYou've done every single RIZAP Challenge!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Huh. So that was the last one?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Yes, the 12th and final challenge is complete!\r\nNow let's see how far you've come!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "So what did you think of RIZAP?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "I'm glad I decided to join.\r\nI didn't expect such a personal touch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "I learned a lot about my diet, too.\r\nYou weren't kidding about being committed to results."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "It's nice to hear such high praise!\r\nMore importantly, today marks your RIZAP graduation!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "However, Kiryu-san! You can re-enroll\r\nas a member whenever you'd like."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "Come talk to me if you're feeling out of shape!\r\nWe can start from the very beginning again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Hopefully it doesn't come to that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Don't be a stranger, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "Ah, Kiryu-san! Are you looking\r\nto re-enroll in the RIZAP program?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "I am..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "I'm feeling kinda rusty, to be honest.\r\nGet me back on the plan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "A wonderful decision!\r\nI'll process your membership right away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "Please talk to me when you want to train!\r\nI'll help you get the body you've always dreamed of!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "(I don't have enough money...\r\nMaybe I should come back later.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "Actually, I was just checking in.\r\nSorry to bother you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "It's no problem.\r\nJust come again if you ever want to train!"
msgstr ""

